Package: msk
Title: Biodiversity Indicators for the Swiss Modular Stepwise Procedure (MSK)
Version: 0.2
Authors@R:
    person("Tobias", "Roth", email = "roth@hintermannweber.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculate biodiversity indicators (alpha, gamma, and beta
    diversity, abundance) from species occurrence data following the Darwin
    Core standard. Designed for data from the Swiss Modular Stepwise
    Procedure (Modulstufenkonzept, MSK) but applicable to any
    event/occurrence dataset.
